NAME:
   flight desktop show - Show information about a desktop session

USAGE:
   flight desktop show [options] <name> 

CATEGORY:
   Sessions

DESCRIPTION:
   Display the connection information for a desktop session.

OPTIONS:
   --help, -h  show help

GLOBAL OPTIONS:
   --log-level LEVEL  set the log LEVEL (debug, info, warn, error, fatal). Default: warn
